{"tid":645229,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"司徒華：即使六四發生，我仍堅決支持「回歸」","createTime":"2018-04-28T03:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T14:32:02.000Z","uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a726045e86618254a46b6d9a5454f081b9a38357","tid":645229,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:02:38.000Z","msg":"司徒華：即使六四發生，我仍堅決支持「回歸」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110221_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110221_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=74fe1800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110231_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110231_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=33edeefb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110236_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110236_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=e2a37cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者：「你指出中國過去幾十年出現很多問題，但在中英會談時，你很早便支持中國收回香港的主權，為什麼呢？」<br />\n<br />\n司徒華：「香港本來就是中國的地方，回歸母體是必然的事實。雖然當時的政權很多地方我並不同意，但假如一個國家對屬於自己的土地也不收回，沒有民族自尊，這個國家和政權是要不得的。我們作為中國人，回歸祖國與十一億人民同命運是很應該的。過去百多年來，我們好像很『僥倖』與中華民族的苦難脫離，但亦有點自咎。所以不論前景如何，我還是支持收回主權，『六‧四』事件並沒有改變我的看法。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; &mdash; 1989年9月1日香港電台節目「新聞天地」專訪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 馮玉蓮《走向九七：政壇精英訪談錄》（1990）<br />\n司徒華回歸香港九七六四<br />\nOne clap, two clap, three clap, forty?<br />\nBy clapping more or less, you can signal to us which stories really stand out.<br />\n<br />\nGo to the profile of Julian Ho 何曦偉<br />\nJulian Ho 何曦偉<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/h0julian\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fh0julian&d=tC8knIg9KEwdQ81Ox3WHHZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=fbc20709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/h0julian</a>"},{"pid":"f4028a533c428f61a0d0c6d72686cd160bca818c","tid":645229,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"@五毛狙擊手<br />\n@LIKLN<br />\n@食魚有魚味<br />\n@真俊華<br />\n@慕清流<br />\n@waiwaiwai<br />\n@波台唔係台<br />\n@求銀祈<br />\n@先知-穆罕默德"},{"pid":"b16271b41ef99a59d46dbd8e8c850e7d49f224a2","tid":645229,"uid":163350,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96f26e3ea64eea1ecce61247f827986a13e6c26c","tid":645229,"uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"害死香港"},{"pid":"5298669ca38373d8e0934f12174c0cb7a6215e64","tid":645229,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"中國人自然<br />\n愛國愛港<br />\n愛中華民族"},{"pid":"bda0c94de3ed2663416957f8c41c5d3d5efd3af0","tid":645229,"uid":89931,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"真千古罪人 司徒華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399b0c6499be950ffc202b3de6a10ec32833a48a","tid":645229,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8690f83c3b950e31a7d1fc12f490f300454960","tid":645229,"uid":60145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"拎番條屍出黎鞭"},{"pid":"136587ce6bd701183f0633f4bae26e105cf084e1","tid":645229,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae640cd321c83f8b8af136083310ae1c9287a3f","tid":645229,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply